      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I have found many use cases where you have large text values that you want to directly use in Java code (e.g. in a unit test where you want to try a method with very long input). So you will often need to paste a large, multi-line String such as a generated Lorem Ipsum text into the Java program. It seems to be in-scope for the IDE to support such an operation without forcing the user to manually break up the text and surround each line with quotes and +."
