    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Okay, I just <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/121199/surround-with-quotation-marks/121513#121513\">found the answer</a> (on Stackoverflow, no less).</p>\n\n<p>Eclipse has an option so that copy-paste of multi-line text into String literals will result in quoted newlines:  </p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Preferences/Java/Editor/Typing/ \"Escape text when pasting into a string literal\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
